{
  "texts": [
    "Therefore, OpenWebText (Gokaslan and Cohen, 2019) replicates the construction method of WebText and open-sources the collected social media data.",
    "Pushshift Reddit (Baumgartner et al, 2020) has been collecting Reddit data since 2015, providing real-time monthly updates to reduce the time costs for researchers.",
    "Chinese social media data is typically collected from platforms such as Zhihu foot_17 and so on.",
    "Zhihu contains high-quality Chinese Q&A pairs and user-created content, making it highly favored for training Chinese LLMs.",
    "Encyclopedia data refers to textual information extracted from encyclopedias, online encyclopedia websites, or other knowledge databases."
  ]
}